---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | JUST RECORD">
  <!-- Dynamic Background Orbs -->
  <div class="bg-orbs">
    <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-3"></div>
  </div>

  <main class="container">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header class="about-header">
      <div class="about-header-content">
        <div class="profile-photo-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/about/profile_portrait.jpg" alt="Profile Portrait" class="profile-photo" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-text-content">
          <h1>1974년 서울에서 태어나,<br/><span class="highlight">차곡차곡 쌓아온 시간의 질감을 기록하는</span><br/>50대 기록가</h1>
          <ul class="about-timeline">
            <li><span>초등학교</span>대길초등학교</li>
            <li><span>중학교</span>윤중중학교</li>
            <li><span>고등학교</span>영신고등학교</li>
            <li><span>대학교</span>아주대학교 경영학과</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="about-intro">
            나이는 단순한 숫자에 불과합니다. 지나온 시간만큼 깊어진 시선으로 매일 새로운 퀘스트를 수행하듯 일상을 즐깁니다.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- My Favorites Section -->
    <section class="favorites stagger-3">
      <h2>My Favorites</h2>
      <div class="favorites-grid bento-grid">
        
        <!-- Gaming (Civ 5) -->
        <div class="favorite-card special hexagon-bg card-civ">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <div class="icon-wrapper hex-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-gamepad-2"><line x1="6" x2="10" y1="12" y2="12"/><line x1="8" x2="8" y1="10" y2="14"/><line x1="15" x2="15.01" y1="13" y2="13"/><line x1="18" x2="18.01" y1="11" y2="11"/><rect width="20" height="12" x="2" y="6" rx="2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>나의 인생 게임: 문명 5</h3>
            <p class="civ-quote">"한 턴만 더... 하던 열정으로 오늘 하루를 기록합니다."</p>
            <p>
              단순한 게임을 넘어선 거대한 서사. 제국을 이끌며 밤을 지새우던 그 전략적인 고민과 즐거움은 이제 제 삶과 기록의 원동력이 되었습니다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Travel -->
        <div class="favorite-card card-travel pattern-dots">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <div class="icon-wrapper">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plane-takeoff"><path d="M2 22h20"/><path d="M6.36 17.4 4 17l-2-4 1.1-.55a2 2 0 0 1 1.8 0l.17.1a2 2 0 0 0 1.8 0L8 12l5-5 1.5-1.5a2.82 2.82 0 1 1 4 4L17 11l-3 6.1a2 2 0 0 1-1.8 1.1H6.36z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Travel</h3>
            <p>새로운 맵을 탐험하듯, 낯선 곳에서의 예상치 못한 만남과 풍경을 즐깁니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Food -->
        <div class="favorite-card card-food pattern-waves">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <div class="icon-wrapper">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-utensils"><path d="M3 2v7c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2"/><path d="M7 2v20"/><path d="M21 15V2v0a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v6c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h3Zm0 0v7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Food</h3>
            <p>맛있는 음식은 체력을 회복시켜주는 훌륭한 포션입니다. 좋은 사람들과 나누는 미식의 기쁨.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Movie -->
        <div class="favorite-card card-movie pattern-lines">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <div class="icon-wrapper">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clapperboard"><path d="M20.2 6 3 11l-.9-2.4c-.3-1.1.3-2.2 1.3-2.5l13.5-4c1.1-.3 2.2.3 2.5 1.3Z"/><path d="m6.2 5.3 3.1 3.9"/><path d="m12.4 3.4 3.1 4"/><path d="M3 11h18v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Movie</h3>
            <p>잘 짜여진 스크립트와 영상미. 2시간 동안 즐기는 또 다른 세계로의 여행.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sports -->
        <div class="favorite-card card-sports pattern-cross">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <div class="icon-wrapper">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Sports</h3>
            <p>신체 나이란 숫자에 불과합니다. 건강한 체력은 모든 열정적인 퀘스트의 기본!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Closing Quote -->
    <section class="closing">
      <blockquote>
        "지나온 발자취를 소중히 여기며,<br/>오늘 하루도 아이처럼 즐겁게 기록합니다."
      </blockquote>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* --- Dynamic Background Orbs --- */
  .bg-orbs {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    z-index: -2;
    overflow: hidden;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-color: #fafdfb;
  }

  .orb {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    opacity: 0.5;
    animation: float 20s infinite ease-in-out alternate;
  }

  .orb-1 {
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(5,150,105,0.1) 0%, rgba(5,150,105,0) 70%);
    top: -10%;
    left: -10%;
  }

  .orb-2 {
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(16,185,129,0.08) 0%, rgba(16,185,129,0) 70%);
    bottom: -10%;
    right: -10%;
    animation-delay: -5s;
    animation-duration: 25s;
  }

  .orb-3 {
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(52,211,153,0.08) 0%, rgba(52,211,153,0) 70%);
    top: 40%;
    left: 30%;
    animation-delay: -10s;
    animation-duration: 30s;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
    100% { transform: translate(100px, 50px) scale(1.2); }
  }

  /* --- Layout & Spacing --- */
  main {
    padding-top: var(--spacing-xxl);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .stagger-1 { opacity: 0; animation: fadeInUp 0.8s forwards 0.2s; }
  .stagger-2 { opacity: 0; animation: fadeInUp 0.8s forwards 0.4s; }
  .stagger-3 { opacity: 0; animation: fadeInUp 0.8s forwards 0.6s; }
  .stagger-4 { opacity: 0; animation: fadeInUp 0.8s forwards 0.8s; }

  .about-header {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xxl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xxl);
    border-bottom: 2px dashed rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
  }

  .about-header-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-xxl);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-header-content {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  .profile-photo-wrapper {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 220px;
    height: 280px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 4px solid #fff;
    box-shadow: 
      0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1),
      inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    transform: rotate(-3deg);
    transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), box-shadow 0.5s ease;
  }

  .profile-photo-wrapper:hover {
    transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.05) translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 
      0 30px 50px rgba(5,150,105,0.15),
      inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(5,150,105,0.2);
  }

  .profile-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .about-text-content {
    flex-grow: 1;
    position: relative;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  h1 .highlight {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: transparent;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-accent) 0%, #10b981 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .about-intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-timeline {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    max-width: fit-content;
    text-align: left;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) var(--spacing-xl);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  .about-timeline li {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-timeline li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -12px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .about-timeline li span {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    width: 70px;
    display: inline-block;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* --- Favorites Section (Bento Grid) --- */
  .favorites {
    padding: var(--spacing-xxxl) 0;
  }

  .bento-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    grid-auto-rows: minmax(180px, auto);
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  /* Bento specific spanning */
  .card-civ { grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 2; }
  .card-travel { grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1; }
  .card-food { grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1; }
  .card-movie { grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 2; }
  .card-sports { grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 1; }

  .favorite-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    border-radius: 24px;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .card-inner {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .favorite-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: 
      0 20px 40px -10px rgba(5,150,105,0.1),
      0 0 0 2px rgba(16,185,129,0.2);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  /* Shine effect sweeping across the card on hover */
  .favorite-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: -150%; width: 50%; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255,255,255,0) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.7) 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);
    transform: skewX(-20deg);
    transition: all 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    z-index: 10;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .favorite-card:hover::before {
    left: 200%;
    transition-duration: 0.8s;
  }

  /* Civ 5 Special Card */
  .favorite-card.special {
    grid-column: 1 / -1; /* Spans full width */
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--color-bg) 0%, var(--color-accent-light) 100%);
    border-color: var(--color-accent-light);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Hexagon background pattern for Civ 5 */
  .hexagon-bg::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    right: -20px;
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='40' height='40' viewBox='0 0 40 40' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M20 0l17.32 10v20L20 40 2.68 30V10z' fill='none' stroke='%23059669' stroke-width='1' stroke-opacity='0.15'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    background-size: 60px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    z-index: 0;
  /* Dynamic Patterns for non-civ cards */
  .pattern-dots::after, .pattern-waves::after, .pattern-lines::after, .pattern-cross::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
    opacity: 0.15;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    border-radius: 24px;
  }
  
  .pattern-dots::after {
    background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(5,150,105,1) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 20px 20px;
  }

  .pattern-waves::after {
    background: repeating-radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, transparent 0, rgba(5,150,105,0.1) 10px, transparent 11px, transparent 20px);
  }

  .pattern-lines::after {
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(5,150,105,0.1) 0, rgba(5,150,105,0.1) 2px, transparent 2px, transparent 10px);
  }

  .pattern-cross::after {
    background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(5,150,105,1) 1px, transparent 1px), radial-gradient(rgba(5,150,105,1) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    background-position: 0 0, 20px 20px;
  }

  .favorite-card.special > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* Hexagon Icon Wrapper */
  .icon-wrapper {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent-light);
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .hex-icon {
    border-radius: 0;
    width: 56px;
    height: 64px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    /* pure CSS hexagon */
    clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 100% 25%, 100% 75%, 50% 100%, 0% 75%, 0% 25%);
  }

  .favorite-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .civ-quote {
    font-size: 1.15rem !important;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-accent-hover) !important;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm) !important;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .favorite-card p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    word-break: keep-all;
  }

  /* --- Closing Quote --- */
  .closing {
    padding: var(--spacing-xxl) 0 var(--spacing-xxxl) 0;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 2px dashed rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s forwards 0.8s;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    word-break: keep-all;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .bento-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    .card-movie { grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1; }
    .card-sports { grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 1; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .bento-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .card-civ, .card-travel, .card-food, .card-movie, .card-sports {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      grid-row: auto;
    }
    .profile-photo-wrapper {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
    .about-timeline {
      margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-lg) auto;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    blockquote {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
